name: FootballArrests
0:
”Alexa, ask Football Arrests for the most common crime on the Jets.”
”Alexa, ask Football Arrests for the team with the most arrests.”
”Alexa, ask Football Arrests for the player with the most arrests on the Giants.”
skdetail:
Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: football arrests
des:
Get detailed NFL arrest data on teams and players based off of the data provided by nflarrest.com. You can ask who has the most arrests on the jets or what is the most common crime on the giants. 

Check out nflarrest.com for more interactive features.







NOTE: This app is not affiliated with nflarrest.com 
NOTE: this skill is in no way affiliated with or endorsed by the NFL
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
